data.description: Enjoy the tranquility of a peaceful neighborhood while being conveniently located near schools, parks, and shopping centers. This 3-bedroom ranch property boasts a solid foundation and timeless charm, it's ready for a makeover to unlock its full potential. This is a fantastic opportunity for those with a vision to create a personalized space that suits their lifestyle. While this home has great bones, (HVAC, Roof, and Kitchen Appliances new in 2021) The kitchen and bathrooms could benefit from a modern touch, with a bit of TLC, this house can be transformed into the perfect blend of comfort and style. Please note that this property requires third-party approval. The sale is subject to the approval of Trustee As-is.
